{
  "message": "test(demo): add responsive breakpoint E2E snapshot tests (bd-130l.6)\n\n6 new snapshot tests covering all 5 breakpoint tiers (Xs\u2192Xl) plus a\nbreakpoint transition validation test. Snapshots at 40x24, 70x24,\n100x30, 130x40, 170x40 verify layout switching from 1 to 3 columns.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
